<h2>Why Bi-Weekly Lawn Service is Ideal for Chicagoland Homes</h2>
<p>For many homeowners in Chicago and the surrounding suburbs, weekly mowing can feel excessive, while monthly service allows for overgrowth and weeds. Bi-weekly maintenance hits the sweet spot.<br/><br/>It promotes healthy, dense turf growth by preventing the lawn from becoming stressed. This schedule is perfectly aligned with the typical growth rate of grass in Illinois during the spring and summer, keeping your yard neat and tidy without fail.</p>

